EN: Please reply to the email I sent you promptly.

ZH: 我正在等待他的回复。
EN: I am waiting for his reply.

ZH: 我不知道该如何回复这个问题。
EN: I don't know how to respond to this question.

ZH: 他迟迟没有回复我的短信。
EN: He hasn't replied to my text message yet.

ZH: 她延迟了几天才回复我的电话。
EN: She took a few days to reply to my phone call.

ZH: 很抱歉我没有及时回复你。
EN: I'm sorry for not replying to you in a timely manner.

ZH: 请回复这封信以确认你的出席。
EN: Please reply to this letter to confirm your attendance.

