EN: He replied in a friendly manner and expressed his gratitude.

ZH: 他的回复很简短，只有一个字。
EN: His reply was very short, only one word.

ZH: 能不能请你回复一下我的微信消息？
EN: Could you please reply to my WeChat message?

ZH: 你能回复一下我的提议吗？
EN: Can you reply to my proposal?

ZH: 我会尽快回复你的邮件。
EN: I will reply to your email as soon as possible.

